body_html: I faced the same problem today (gtx1080, cuda 9.2, tfversion = 1.12.0). So in my case, I was running Jupyter notebook , and then I tried running my other script, that's when the error was thrown. What Solved is, like @RoytenBerge said, shutting down the jupyter kernal.
